Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.53,0:00:08.54,Main,guy 1,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}The ice here is in the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.54,0:00:10.84,Main,guy 2,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Then why don't we have\Ntwo boats set off here,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.84,0:00:13.06,Main,guy 2,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}and have this boat circle around?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.17,0:00:13.06,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Tomorrow's finally come...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.38,0:00:16.33,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Preparations sure go by fast \Nwhen adults are around.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.33,0:00:17.76,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, definitely.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.76,0:00:18.87,Main,akari,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for your hard work.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.16,0:00:20.86,Main,akari,0000,0000,0000,,I brought a present.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.13,0:00:22.82,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.82,0:00:24.37,Main,akari,0000,0000,0000,,Though it's just unsold bread.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.65,0:00:26.07,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}It's plenty.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.90,0:00:26.56,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,You're such a good boy \Nfor running errands.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.11,0:00:29.09,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.01,0:00:32.34,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,Akira-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.66,0:00:34.72,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Hasn't he been weird lately?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.50,0:00:36.76,Main,akari,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.78,0:00:41.90,Main,tsumu,0000,0000,0000,,This should be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.90,0:00:43.80,Main,sayu,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Akira, you're here, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.48,0:00:47.64,Main,kaname,0000,0000,0000,,Come to think of it, this'll be\NAkira-kun's first time at an Ofunehiki.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.06,0:00:50.32,Main,sayu,0000,0000,0000,,Well, we hadn't done one for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.29,0:00:52.86,Main,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,Do you want to take a closer look?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.40,0:00:55.67,Main,akira,0000,0000,0000,,Namaka's.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.67,0:00:56.49,Main,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.89,0:00:58.63,Main,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,This pendant...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.20,0:01:01.37,Main,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,is filled with Manaka-san's love.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.23,0:01:03.98,Main,akira,0000,0000,0000,,Namaka's love...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.64,0:01:07.44,Main,kaname,0000,0000,0000,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.81,0:01:08.91,Main,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,Akira!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.64,0:01:16.76,Main,sayu,0000,0000,0000,,Miuna!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.60,0:01:20.49,Italics,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,It's so fast...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.01,0:01:21.93,Italics,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.17,0:01:24.01,Italics,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,There's not even a current...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.43,0:01:25.05,Italics,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.46,0:01:28.32,Main,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,It's melting!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.98,0:01:34.38,Italics,voice,0000,0000,0000,,I love Hii-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.28,0:01:36.69,Italics,voice,0000,0000,0000,,I love Hii-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.46,0:01:39.74,Flashback,voice,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1,558)}I love Hii-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.02,0:01:43.34,Main,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,"I love...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.57,0:01:45.44,Main,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,Hii-kun..."
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.22,0:01:47.41,Main,tsumu,0000,0000,0000,,I knew it.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.61,0:01:48.28,Main,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,Tsumugu?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.96,0:01:49.95,Main,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,"Knew it"?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.26,0:01:51.28,Main,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.06,0:01:54.55,Flashback,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,I admired it.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.03,0:01:58.45,Flashback,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,Beyond the sea, beyond the sky...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.94,0:02:01.55,Flashback,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,The sun that was so far, far away.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.46,0:02:03.70,Flashback,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,It was so bright.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.17,0:02:05.45,Flashback,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,It shined down on me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.74,0:02:07.00,Flashback,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,It made me warm.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.43,0:02:08.76,Flashback,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,It made me excited.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.06,0:02:10.94,Flashback,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.00,0:02:12.59,Flashback,tsumu,0000,0000,0000,,"But"?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.72,0:02:27.00,Flashback,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,Hii-kun's the sea.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.58,0:02:28.29,Flashback,tsumu,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.73,0:02:31.49,Flashback,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,When I came out of the sea,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.87,0:02:36.13,Flashback,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,the surface that was filled with sunlight was so much fun, and exciting...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.06,0:02:38.91,Flashback,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,But... I realized it's \Nbecause the sea was there...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.57,0:02:43.93,Flashback,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,that's why I was able \Nto admire the surface.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.14,0:02:47.39,Flashback,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,If I'm not by the sea,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.70,0:02:50.42,Flashback,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,my Ena dries up, and I can't breathe.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.34,0:02:53.65,Flashback,tsumu,0000,0000,0000,,Does that mean you love Hikari?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.25,0:02:59.52,Flashback,tsumu,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you crying?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.01,0:03:03.40,Flashback,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,Because I know how Chii-chan feels...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.40,0:03:03.94,Flashback,tsumu,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.92,0:03:07.49,Flashback,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,She said not to tell anyone \Nthat she likes Hii-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.61,0:03:12.08,Flashback,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want you to \Ntell anyone either...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.62,0:03:14.85,Flashback,tsumu,0000,0000,0000,,Are you sure that's what you want?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.80,0:03:22.71,Main,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,Why...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.15,0:03:26.05,Main,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,Why didn't you say \Nanything this whole time?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.72,0:03:28.43,Main,tsumu,0000,0000,0000,,Because she asked me \Nnot to say anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.52,0:03:30.71,Main,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.71,0:03:32.53,Main,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,Hikari's worked so hard!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.94,0:03:35.81,Main,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,He believed Manaka-san's \Nlove was for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.30,0:03:39.70,Main,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,He really worked so \Nhard to get it back...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.57,0:03:41.84,Main,tsumu,0000,0000,0000,,Hikari said it himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.44,0:03:44.33,Main,tsumu,0000,0000,0000,,To get Mukaido's feelings back,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.62,0:03:47.50,Main,tsumu,0000,0000,0000,,the person she loves has to work for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.36,0:03:50.12,Main,tsumu,0000,0000,0000,,If that's the case,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.62,0:03:52.70,Main,tsumu,0000,0000,0000,,Hikari's already done more than enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.89,0:03:56.54,Main,tsumu,0000,0000,0000,,Love is probably like the sea.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.29,0:03:58.84,Main,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,Love and the sea?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.66,0:04:01.84,Main,tsumu,0000,0000,0000,,It's not just all fun and love...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.84,0:04:04.43,Main,tsumu,0000,0000,0000,,You also have to embrace the sadness,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.80,0:04:06.51,Main,tsumu,0000,0000,0000,,pain, and everything else...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.46,0:04:09.74,Main,tsumu,0000,0000,0000,,That's when new feelings are born.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.48,0:04:14.71,Italics,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,So it wasn't...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.58,0:04:16.73,Italics,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,one-sided...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.77,0:04:20.78,Episode-Title - Copy,epi,0000,0000,0000,,Episode Twenty-Five:\NLove is Like the Sea
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.33,0:04:24.48,Italics,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,Hikari and Manaka-san \Nloved each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.38,0:04:30.06,Italics,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,If Manaka-san gets back the ability to love someone after the Ofunehiki...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.37,0:04:32.53,Italics,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,Then...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.62,0:04:34.83,Italics,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,Then...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.57,0:04:45.46,Main,kaname,0000,0000,0000,,I have something I want \Nto talk to you about.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.90,0:04:46.84,Main,kaname,0000,0000,0000,,Is that all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.17,0:04:53.24,Main,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, Manaka-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.64,0:04:56.17,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,No, it's my fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.62,0:04:59.06,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,Because I don't understand what love is.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.42,0:05:00.21,Main,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.78,0:05:05.88,Main,muna,0000,0000,0000,,Manaka-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.81,0:05:08.78,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,The sound of waves won't go away.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.08,0:05:11.38,Main,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,Sound of waves?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.32,0:05:21.87,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,When you do that, Miuna-chan,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.88,0:05:24.32,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,for some reason,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.32,0:05:25.67,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,I feel a little better...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.69,0:05:30.68,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,Can we stay like this for a while?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.68,0:05:42.48,Main,tsumu,0000,0000,0000,,Chisaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.45,0:05:44.42,Main,tsumu,0000,0000,0000,,Can I come in?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.84,0:05:45.66,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.66,0:05:46.79,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.98,0:05:49.06,Main,tsumu,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.76,0:05:52.70,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,It's the outfit we're wearing\N as the Ojoshi-sama's attendants.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.70,0:05:55.26,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,I thought I'd adjust the hems a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.24,0:05:58.61,Main,tsumu,0000,0000,0000,,I heard from Kaname.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.91,0:05:59.58,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.06,0:06:01.36,Main,tsumu,0000,0000,0000,,About your feelings.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.36,0:06:03.84,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What are you...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.84,0:06:05.49,Main,tsumu,0000,0000,0000,,You don't have to lie...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.49,0:06:06.37,Main,tsumu,0000,0000,0000,,about anything anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.54,0:06:07.73,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.73,0:06:09.76,Main,tsumu,0000,0000,0000,,Not only you, but Mukaido as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.37,0:06:12.02,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.94,0:06:23.04,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,Manaka loves Hikari...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.01,0:06:28.75,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,I really am awful...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.03,0:06:31.16,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,I've hoped...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.37,0:06:34.90,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,since a long time ago, and even now...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.77,0:06:39.17,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,that Hikari would always love Manaka.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.92,0:06:42.98,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,And that Manaka would always \Nbe protected by Hikari.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.83,0:06:45.60,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't want anything to change
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.60,0:06:47.68,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,between the four of us because \Nwe loved each other so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.17,0:06:49.82,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,I really wanted Hikari and Manaka
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.82,0:06:51.66,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,to be in love with each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.58,0:06:54.80,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,Because that would keep\Nour relationship unchanged
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.14,0:06:57.33,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,from how it's always been.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.74,0:06:59.18,Main,tsumu,0000,0000,0000,,That's not the case now.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.84,0:07:03.32,Main,tsumu,0000,0000,0000,,It's not because you wanted to protect \Nthe relationships between you four.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.28,0:07:05.81,Main,tsumu,0000,0000,0000,,You're in love with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.63,0:07:09.50,Main,tsumu,0000,0000,0000,,That's why you were hoping \Nthat they loved each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.10,0:07:12.53,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,You think way too highly of yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.26,0:07:15.66,Main,tsumu,0000,0000,0000,,That's just what I thought \Nwhen I tied it all together.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.96,0:07:17.03,Main,tsumu,0000,0000,0000,,Was I wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.28,0:07:20.21,Main,tsumu,0000,0000,0000,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.56,0:07:21.98,Main,tsumu,0000,0000,0000,,I'll think it over again.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.40,0:07:29.44,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,Are you really still thinking about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.69,0:07:31.61,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,About who I really love?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.61,0:07:35.18,Main,tsumu,0000,0000,0000,,No, I still think that \Nyou're in love with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.39,0:07:39.84,Main,tsumu,0000,0000,0000,,But I'm trying to figure out \Nhow to get you to admit it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.61,0:07:44.84,Main,tsumu,0000,0000,0000,,I'm serious.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.25,0:07:46.49,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.17,0:07:49.89,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,You're not going to deny it this time?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.62,0:07:56.91,Main,tsumu,0000,0000,0000,,Can I hold you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.66,0:08:05.54,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.68,0:08:07.62,Main,tsumu,0000,0000,0000,,Chisaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.29,0:08:12.27,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,No, no, no...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.72,0:08:16.01,Italics,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,I can't be the only happy one...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.09,0:08:17.98,Italics,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.98,0:08:26.19,Sea Salt,sign,0000,0000,0000,,Sea Salt
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.12,0:08:55.03,Main,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,Hikari!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.68,0:09:05.64,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.93,0:09:08.96,Main,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,Hikari, where are you going...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.96,0:09:10.10,Main,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,at this hour?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.10,0:09:13.01,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,I just thought I'd go \Ncheck out the boat.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.01,0:09:14.06,Main,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,The boat?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.06,0:09:16.16,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,I was just thinking that \Ntomorrow's the day.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.63,0:09:19.21,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,So I wanted to make sure we didn't \Nmiss anything in the preparations.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.67,0:09:23.66,Main,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,I hope Manaka-san's love comes back...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.40,0:09:26.06,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,But that's not the only thing at stake.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.32,0:09:28.92,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Hopefully we'll be able to do \Nsomething about the surface, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.91,0:09:31.84,Main,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, but I hope it comes back.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.12,0:09:34.84,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Apparently that's all girls think about.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.67,0:09:37.17,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,You should be more concerned \Nabout the bigger pict—
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.17,0:09:38.78,Main,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,You love Manaka-san, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.78,0:09:41.32,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What are you talking abou—
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.32,0:09:42.38,Main,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,You love her, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.25,0:09:47.25,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.25,0:09:48.22,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.89,0:09:52.08,Main,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,Say it more!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.73,0:09:53.75,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.36,0:09:55.57,Main,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,Say it more.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.57,0:09:57.01,Main,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,Say that you love Manaka-san more.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.01,0:09:58.93,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,A-Are you stupid?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.93,0:09:59.84,Main,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,Say it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.04,0:10:01.85,Main,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,In return for all the \Nthings I've done for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.85,0:10:03.38,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,What kinds of things are you into?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.86,0:10:07.82,Main,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,Say it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.01,0:10:09.82,Main,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,Please...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.44,0:10:16.98,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,I'm in love with Manaka.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.98,0:10:17.68,Main,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,More!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.22,0:10:19.83,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,I love Manaka.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.83,0:10:20.57,Main,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,More...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.66,0:10:22.60,Main,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,More!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.94,0:10:24.92,Main,hkari,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, would you give it a res—
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.37,0:10:30.36,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Miuna?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.62,0:10:34.24,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Where are you—
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.24,0:10:35.21,Main,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going home!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.41,0:10:41.40,Italics,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,It hurts...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.32,0:10:45.90,Italics,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,The love that I feel \Nfor Hikari... hurts.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.67,0:10:49.75,Italics,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,It needs to hurt more and more,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.48,0:10:53.04,Italics,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,to push my feelings for \NHikari to a breaking point,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.80,0:10:55.29,Italics,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,so I can feel like throwing them away.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.05,0:10:58.09,Italics,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,And then, will I...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.22,0:11:05.12,Italics,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,Will I be able to give up on Hikari?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.49,0:11:25.95,Nishiura,sign,0000,0000,0000,,Nishiura
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.78,0:11:25.18,Main,tsumu,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.18,0:11:27.18,Main,driver,0000,0000,0000,,Congrats, old man Kihara.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.18,0:11:28.85,Main,driver,0000,0000,0000,,Glad to hear that you're \Nfinally allowed to go out.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.58,0:11:31.12,Main,gramps,0000,0000,0000,,It's finally time.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.32,0:11:40.72,Main,sayu,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so nervous!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.72,0:11:42.70,Main,sayu,0000,0000,0000,,I need to check the program.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.70,0:11:44.63,Main,akari,0000,0000,0000,,All right, look up a little.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.02,0:11:45.42,Main,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,O-Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.69,0:11:46.63,Main,akari,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.77,0:11:47.69,Main,sayu,0000,0000,0000,,So...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.69,0:11:50.13,Main,sayu,0000,0000,0000,,first we need to get the sacred \Nfire from Uroko-sama...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.09,0:11:54.68,Main,akari,0000,0000,0000,,This time, the Ofunehiki won't \Nhave any help from the sea.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.68,0:11:57.02,Main,akari,0000,0000,0000,,So it's different from usual \Nand a bit complicated...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.88,0:12:00.90,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,Akira-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.31,0:12:04.25,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.25,0:12:07.25,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,There's something I forgot to tell you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.16,0:12:11.90,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for the letter.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.12,0:12:21.27,Main,akira,0000,0000,0000,,Kancho!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.59,0:12:25.66,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,Jeez...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.02,0:12:28.29,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,So love means...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.01,0:12:30.71,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,thank you...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.17,0:12:41.57,Main,kaname,0000,0000,0000,,Really, that outfit...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.92,0:12:44.72,Main,kaname,0000,0000,0000,,looks so much better on adults \Nthan junior high kids.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.72,0:12:45.84,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,Kaname.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.35,0:12:47.40,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.40,0:12:47.84,Main,kaname,0000,0000,0000,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.62,0:12:49.66,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.49,0:12:52.54,Main,kaname,0000,0000,0000,,Because I played telephone with Tsumugu?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.01,0:12:54.33,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,About a lot of things.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.42,0:12:58.09,Main,kaname,0000,0000,0000,,Chisaki, you're not thinking \Nanything weird, are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.09,0:12:58.58,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.50,0:13:02.21,Main,kaname,0000,0000,0000,,Like thinking that you'll become the \NOjoshi-sama instead this time...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.01,0:13:06.93,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,All of us were always together.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.53,0:13:09.32,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,Then I was the only \None on the surface...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.32,0:13:10.18,Main,kaname,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.81,0:13:13.90,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,Kaname.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.64,0:13:15.62,Main,kaname,0000,0000,0000,,You can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.31,0:13:21.10,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.42,0:13:23.44,Main,person,0000,0000,0000,,Uroko-sama has arrived!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.41,0:13:37.63,Main,itaru,0000,0000,0000,,This way, Uroko-sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.63,0:13:38.79,Main,uroko,0000,0000,0000,,For the love of...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.02,0:13:42.18,Main,uroko,0000,0000,0000,,How dare you trap me \Nin such a small space?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.50,0:13:47.23,Main,uroko,0000,0000,0000,,Hm...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.46,0:13:48.76,Main,uroko,0000,0000,0000,,Not bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.38,0:13:50.52,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,You sound all important.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.73,0:13:53.47,Main,uroko,0000,0000,0000,,That's because I am important. \NIt can't be helped.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.13,0:13:58.14,Main,uroko,0000,0000,0000,,So that's the Ojoshi.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.14,0:14:01.16,Main,uroko,0000,0000,0000,,Just like every other time, it \Nlooks nothing like the real thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.16,0:14:04.45,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,So the original Ojoshi \Nwas a lot prettier?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.62,0:14:06.54,Main,uroko,0000,0000,0000,,No, not at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.76,0:14:07.38,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.77,0:14:10.26,Main,uroko,0000,0000,0000,,She was a shrimp with \Nfreckles everywhere,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.26,0:14:12.16,Main,uroko,0000,0000,0000,,and her body was weak...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.61,0:14:15.20,Main,uroko,0000,0000,0000,,Though they call it a sacrifice,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.20,0:14:17.20,Main,uroko,0000,0000,0000,,I'm assuming for the \Nhumans on the surface,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.20,0:14:20.41,Main,uroko,0000,0000,0000,,it was a convenient way \Nto get rid of some people.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.68,0:14:23.65,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,You... loved the Ojoshi, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.80,0:14:26.07,Main,uroko,0000,0000,0000,,Well, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.85,0:14:30.94,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Before you fell off the Sea God, \Nyou were the same person...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.94,0:14:32.21,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,or rather, the same god, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.31,0:14:38.12,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Was it really okay to return \NOjoshi-sama to the surface like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.16,0:14:41.74,Main,uroko,0000,0000,0000,,I was more...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.74,0:14:45.28,Main,uroko,0000,0000,0000,,around the Sea God's \Nshoulder blade area.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.62,0:14:46.40,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.74,0:14:49.58,Main,uroko,0000,0000,0000,,If I were the right hand's scale,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.58,0:14:52.12,Main,uroko,0000,0000,0000,,I could have touched her hair.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.42,0:14:54.05,Main,uroko,0000,0000,0000,,If I were on the left hand,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.05,0:14:56.68,Main,uroko,0000,0000,0000,,I could have held her.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.22,0:15:02.29,Main,uroko,0000,0000,0000,,However, as soon as I fell off, the \NSea God became something distinct.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.15,0:15:05.86,Main,uroko,0000,0000,0000,,Once that happened, I \Nbecame but a mere scale...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.86,0:15:08.43,Main,uroko,0000,0000,0000,,Not to mention a scale \Nof a shoulder blade.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.43,0:15:10.62,Main,uroko,0000,0000,0000,,What could I speak of the Ojoshi?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.90,0:15:13.24,Main,person,0000,0000,0000,,Uroko-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.24,0:15:15.42,Main,person,0000,0000,0000,,It's about to begin so please...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.53,0:15:23.13,Main,uroko,0000,0000,0000,,So show me, Hikari.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.22,0:15:26.35,Main,uroko,0000,0000,0000,,What you're able to change,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.88,0:15:29.17,Main,uroko,0000,0000,0000,,and what you are not.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.72,0:15:41.88,Main,teach,0000,0000,0000,,Look, it's Hikari and the others.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.26,0:15:43.96,Main,teach,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.96,0:15:46.54,Main,teach,0000,0000,0000,,Do your best!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.27,0:16:39.48,Main,uroko,0000,0000,0000,,Sea God...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.17,0:16:44.24,Main,uroko,0000,0000,0000,,How will you respond to the \Nworkings of your children?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.94,0:17:24.02,Main,priest,0000,0000,0000,,Under your divine benevolence,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.20,0:17:26.34,Main,uroko,0000,0000,0000,,we, the people of Shioshishio,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.34,0:17:29.37,Main,uroko,0000,0000,0000,,have always respected, honored and served
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.37,0:17:32.73,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,our father, our god, the mighty Sea God,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.73,0:17:36.64,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,throughout the years since the beginning of time.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.94,0:17:39.34,Main,uroko,0000,0000,0000,,O Sea God, most exalted one,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.34,0:17:43.88,Main,uroko,0000,0000,0000,,protect us, your children. \NBless us, and give us prosperity.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.36,0:17:45.89,Main,gramps,0000,0000,0000,,A storm's coming...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.78,0:18:16.17,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,The lull of the sea...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.33,0:18:26.43,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Manaka!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.87,0:18:28.00,Main,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,Manaka-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.18,0:18:32.35,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,I have to save her!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.54,0:18:34.28,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,Manaka doesn't have Ena!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.28,0:18:35.21,Main,kaname,0000,0000,0000,,Chisaki!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.94,0:18:38.93,Main,sayu,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.36,0:18:43.31,Main,sayu,0000,0000,0000,,Kaname!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.31,0:18:45.01,Main,kaname,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone, hold onto the boat!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.70,0:18:47.15,Main,guy,0000,0000,0000,,Don't get thrown off!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.79,0:18:53.87,Main,itaru,0000,0000,0000,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.87,0:18:54.86,Main,akira,0000,0000,0000,,Namaka!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.85,0:19:01.60,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Miuna!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.81,0:19:02.89,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Get Manaka!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.46,0:19:04.53,Main,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,Hikari!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.78,0:19:12.56,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,It's so hard to breathe in the sea...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.00,0:19:14.18,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,It's so rough...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.18,0:19:15.06,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,it hurts.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.29,0:19:16.25,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,I'm scared...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.57,0:19:19.33,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,The sea that had always \Nprotected me is...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.04,0:19:21.01,Main,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,Manaka-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.82,0:19:25.85,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,Miuna-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.94,0:19:30.35,Main,tsumu,0000,0000,0000,,The sea is responding \Nto Miuna's feelings.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.53,0:19:31.60,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.12,0:19:33.71,Main,tsumu,0000,0000,0000,,Mukaido loves Hikari...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.41,0:19:36.11,Main,tsumu,0000,0000,0000,,And so does Miuna.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.72,0:19:39.96,Main,tsumu,0000,0000,0000,,Mukaido's feelings and Miuna's \Nfeelings are very similar.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.21,0:19:43.61,Main,tsumu,0000,0000,0000,,That's why Mukaido's feelings that \Nmelted into the sea are shining.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.29,0:19:45.36,Main,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,Manaka-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.61,0:19:57.58,Italics,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,I understand...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.04,0:19:59.60,Italics,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,I can sense them.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.60,0:20:01.20,Italics,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,I can feel your feelings, Manaka-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.96,0:20:02.96,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,I knew it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.64,0:20:06.72,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,When I'm with you like this, Miuna-chan,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.24,0:20:08.99,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,I feel so at ease.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.56,0:20:13.46,Main,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,That's because my Ena is \Nshouting that it loves Hikari.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.46,0:20:14.17,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.07,0:20:16.50,Main,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,Not just Hikari,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.89,0:20:20.96,Main,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,but it's shouting that it loves \Nthe sea and everyone else.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.49,0:20:38.48,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Manaka!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.36,0:20:40.13,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Chisaki!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.13,0:20:41.24,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Take care of Manaka!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.24,0:20:42.26,Main,tsumu,0000,0000,0000,,Hikari!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.74,0:20:52.11,Main,uroko,0000,0000,0000,,This presence...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.58,0:21:10.61,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.40,0:21:13.04,Main,tsumu,0000,0000,0000,,The Ojoshi-samas' graveyard?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.86,0:21:16.80,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Miuna!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.96,0:21:23.34,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Miuna!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.04,0:21:39.10,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Sea God, you bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.98,0:21:38.66,Main,tsumu,0000,0000,0000,,Hikari!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.39,0:21:42.33,Main,tsumu,0000,0000,0000,,Hikari!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.53,0:21:44.96,Italics,voice,0000,0000,0000,,I love Hii-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.96,0:21:46.34,Italics,voice,0000,0000,0000,,I love Hii-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.34,0:21:49.06,Italics,voice,0000,0000,0000,,I love Hii-kun. I love Hii-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.06,0:21:50.71,Italics,voice,0000,0000,0000,,I love Hii-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.37,0:21:56.44,Italics,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,Hikari...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.50,0:21:58.32,Italics,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,I love you...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.13,0:22:02.13,Italics,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,I love...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.38,0:22:04.39,Italics,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,Hikari...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.92,0:22:09.02,Italics,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,I love... you
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.50,0:22:12.05,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Miuna!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.79,0:23:33.36,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,Love is like the sea...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.68,0:23:34.25,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,If she didn't love me...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.47,0:23:35.65,Main,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,I'm glad I fell in love with you...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.85,0:23:37.26,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,"Miuna"... the beautiful sea...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.26,0:23:40.71,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,The calmed sea begins to move.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.10,0:23:40.06,Episode-Title,sign,0000,0000,0000,,Final Episode:\NThe Color of the Sea. The Color of the Earth. The Color of the Wind. The Color of Your Heart. Your Color.
